{"telemetry_stream": "UPTIME: 2026-03-20T19:22:10.494Z | CPU: 55% | RAM: 16%", "lore_stream": "RADIO FREEDOM: Attention all Minutemen. Reports of a feral ghoul problem at the old Ridley Creek farm. Help requested. +++ SCAVENGER LOG: The Media ruins are full of Rad-Scorpions. +++ THREE DOG: Coming to you loud and proud from the Chevy Chase ruins! This is GNR, and I\u2019m here for you, children. +++ TRAVIS MILES: Uh, I guess... theres a rumor of a big green monster near the Common? Maybe stay away? If you want? +++ SECURITY: Patrols found a tunnel being dug behind the Nuka-Cola machine. Leads to a dead end. Good. +++ NCR INTELLIGENCE: Remnants of the 5th Battalion spotted near the Appalachian border. They are looking for a way home. +++ INCIDENT: Final Entry. +++ NCR INTELLIGENCE: Trade caravans with NCR seals have been hijacked. The Gun Runners are offering a bounty on the thieves. +++ ADVISORY: Mandatory Blue Route decontamination protocols are now in effect for all returning scouts. +++ LEGEND: The Master once sought a way to evolve all dwellers. He was defeated by a single soul. +++ SECURITY: Found a Secret tunnel to Vault 102. It\u2019s Empty. And Creepy. +++ LOCAL VIBE: The wind howling through the hollowed-out SEPTA cars sounds like a choir of the damned. +++ DWELLER LOG: I miss the sound of rain that doesnt make your skin itch. +++ BLACK MOUNTAIN RADIO: Human-dom is over! Best Friend Tabitha says the era of the Utobitha is here! +++ DWELLER LOG: Ive forgotten what a Tree looks like. I mean, a green one. +++ SIGHTING: A Deathclaw was seen Sleeping in a Car. +++ NCR INTELLIGENCE: President Kimball\u2019s latest speech was met with silence in the outer territories. The Republic is stretched thin. +++ SIGNAL: A Pre-War commercial for Abraxo Cleaner is looping on the emergency band. +++ SECURITY: Unauthorized Radio Free Marple broadcast detected on the internal comms. Signal traced to a toaster. +++ DWELLER LOG: I miss Daylight. The Artificial light is Too Bright. +++ SECURITY: Unauthorized Holotape found in the library. Title: The Truth About Vault-Tec. Incinerated. +++ LEGEND: The Chosen One once dismantled an oil rig with a single explosive charge. +++ SECURITY: Confiscated a Modified Pip-Boy from the machine shop. It was tuned to Enclave balloons. +++ SUPPLY UPDATE: Fancy Lads Snack Cakes are now 200 years past their expiration date. Still delicious. +++ DWELLER LOG: I found a Pre-War nickel. I\u2019m Rich in a Dead world. +++ COMMUNIQUE: Happiness is a requirement. Misery is a fireable offense. +++ LEGEND: The Master was defeated by a Single Soul with a Speech skill of 100. +++ SUPPLY UPDATE: Stoney Lonesome water reserves are at 104%. The purification chip is holding. +++ DWELLER LOG: I miss Daylight. The Glow of the Amber screen is my only Sun. +++ MAINTENANCE: The air filtration system is emitting a smell of Old World Cinnamon. Investigation pending. +++ INCIDENT: The Vault Library has been Categorized by smell. History smells like Dust and Sadness. +++ INCIDENT: Dweller #122 tried to Fly off the Catwalk. Gravity won. +++ ADVISORY: Please refrain from using Abraxo Cleaner as a substitute for toothpaste. Your enamel is not a floor. +++ SUPPLY UPDATE: Purified Water is now available in Metal flavor. +++ LEGEND: A Mysterious Stranger appears when you least expect him. Usually with a .44. +++ BROTHERHOOD OF STEEL: Ad Victoriam is now the official greeting, goodbye, and toast of the Chapter. +++ WARNING: Mirelurk Kings have a voice like an angel. A very angry, sonic-blasting angel. +++ MAINTENANCE: The Geiger Counter in the lobby is clicking. It\u2019s probably just a ghost. +++ INCIDENT: The Elevator stopped between floors for 6 hours. Dweller #302 has emerged as a new person. +++ SUPPLY UPDATE: Med-X supplies are low. Please try Deep Breathing instead. +++ DWELLER LOG: I think the Overseer is a Synth. He doesnt Blink when he Talks. +++ SIGHTING: A Caravan Guard was seen fighting off a Deathclaw with a rolling pin. +++ DWELLER LOG: I think the Machine Spirit is Hungry. I gave it a Paperclip. +++ RAIDER WATCH: The Tunnel Snakes have been wiped out by a pack of Rad-Roaches. Justice is served. +++ SIGNAL: A Pre-War signal is broadcasting The Silver Shroud radio play. +++ SECURITY: Patrols found a Secret room behind the Overseers office. It\u2019s full of Toilet Paper. +++ FOLLOWERS OF THE APOCALYPSE: A small group has set up a clinic in a rusted bus. They are trading medicine for history books. +++ SUPPLY UPDATE: Sugar Bomb stocks are critical. Substitutions will be made with Cram flavored gelatin. +++ RECOVERY: Found a Lunchbox. It contained a Plastic Spoon and a Nuclear Pulse. +++ TRAVIS MILES: So, theres a radio station... this one... and Im talking on it. This is Diamond City Radio. I think.", "timestamp": "21:29:11", "vault_integrity": "STABLE", "disks": [{"name": "disk1", "temp": null, "temp_c": null, "status": "DISK_OK", "size_tb": 14.0, "size_human": "14.00 TB", "size_display": "14.00 TB", "device": "sdc", "type": "DATA", "rotational": true, "isSpinning": false, "idx": 1, "fsType": "xfs"}, {"name": "disk2", "temp": null, "temp_c": null, "status": "DISK_OK", "size_tb": 14.0, "size_human": "14.00 TB", "size_display": "14.00 TB", "device": "sdf", "type": "DATA", "rotational": true, "isSpinning": false, "idx": 2, "fsType": "xfs"}, {"name": "disk3", "temp": null, "temp_c": null, "status": "DISK_OK", "size_tb": 14.0, "size_human": "14.00 TB", "size_display": "14.00 TB", "device": "sdk", "type": "DATA", "rotational": true, "isSpinning": false, "idx": 3, "fsType": "xfs"}, {"name": "disk4", "temp": 40, "temp_c": 40, "status": "DISK_OK", "size_tb": 10.0, "size_human": "10.00 TB", "size_display": "10.00 TB", "device": "sdl", "type": "DATA", "rotational": true, "isSpinning": true, "idx": 4, "fsType": "xfs"}, {"name": "disk5", "temp": null, "temp_c": null, "status": "DISK_OK", "size_tb": 10.0, "size_human": "10.00 TB", "size_display": "10.00 TB", "device": "sdb", "type": "DATA", "rotationa